and to change the selected language.
.Sp
Thereby, each language has a unique internal number.
.Sp
The original distribution contains the following seven languages:
.Sp
.Vb 7
\&            1   ==>   English                     (default)
\&            2   ==>   Français    (French)
\&            3   ==>   Deutsch     (German)
\&            4   ==>   Español     (Spanish)
\&            5   ==>   Português   (Portuguese)
\&            6   ==>   Nederlands  (Dutch)
\&            7   ==>   Italiano    (Italian)
